highlights.text: KPop Demon Hunters Cast has the most spots on Viral Songs Norway. “Golden” is the highest at #11.
“No Lie” by Harry T is the highest new entry on Viral Songs Norway at #3.
“No Broke Boys” by Disco Lines and Tinashe has been on Viral Songs Norway the longest, at 81 days straight.
“Gutta i fra nord” by ID-AI is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs Norway, up 26 spots at #55.
